edu.mccc.cos210.ds

Class PriorityQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mccc.cos210.ds.QueueSingle<E>
      • edu.mccc.cos210.ds.PriorityQueue<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueueInt<E>, Cloneable

    public class PriorityQueue<E>
extends QueueSingle<E>
implements Cloneable
    The PriorityQueue implements the Queue interface by building a heap in an ArrayList. The heap is structured so that the "smallest" item is at the top.
